## Development

### Prerequisites

- Node.js >= 20
- Bun (recommended) or npm/yarn
- **iOS:** Xcode 15+, CocoaPods
- **Android:** Android Studio, JDK 17+

### Setup

```sh
# Clone the repository
git clone {{homepage}}.git
cd {{projectName}}

# Install dependencies
bun install

# Build the library
cd packages/{{projectName}}
bun run build

# Run example app
cd ../../example
bun install
bun run ios # or bun run android
```

